[name]
UTF-8 handling in verbatim text

[options]
utf8 1

[input]
=encoding utf-8

=head1 BEYONCÉ

Beyoncé!  Beyoncé!  Beyoncé!!

    Beyoncé!  Beyoncé!
      Beyoncé!  Beyoncé!
        Beyoncé!  Beyoncé!

Older versions did not convert Beyoncé in verbatim.

[output]
.SH BEYONCÉ
.IX Header "BEYONCÉ"
Beyoncé!  Beyoncé!  Beyoncé!!
.PP
.Vb 3
\&    Beyoncé!  Beyoncé!
\&      Beyoncé!  Beyoncé!
\&        Beyoncé!  Beyoncé!
.Ve
.PP
Older versions did not convert Beyoncé in verbatim.
